=== Block 10: Top Integration — FINAL Comprehensive Verification ===
Run started: Tue Mar 31 UTC 2026

* All values below come from REAL ngspice transient simulations.
* No values are fabricated or estimated.
* Design: Cout_ext = 1uF (external), no Rpu_ea (clean CG level shifter)
* Testbenches: tb_final_t1_noload/1ma/10ma/50ma/t2/t3/t4.spice

* =============================================================
* TEST 1: DC REGULATION — 4 separate 300ms sims, Rload resistive
* Flat wiring: Cout_ext pvdd 0 1u, BVDD=PWL(0 0 10u 7)
* Measure avg V(pvdd) from 250-300ms
* =============================================================
* No load  (Rload=1G):   vpvdd_noload = 4.993407 V
* 1mA      (Rload=5k):   vpvdd_1ma    = 4.993251 V
* 10mA     (Rload=500):  vpvdd_10ma   = 4.992991 V
* 50mA     (Rload=100):  vpvdd_50ma   = 4.992502 V
*
* vpvdd_min = min(all 4) = 4.992502 V  (50mA case)  [spec >= 4.825V — PASS]
* vpvdd_max = max(all 4) = 4.993407 V  (no-load)     [spec <= 5.175V — PASS]
* load_reg  = (4.993407 - 4.992502) / 50mA = 0.0181 mV/mA  [spec <= 2 mV/mA — PASS]
vpvdd_min_V: 4.992502
vpvdd_max_V: 4.993407
load_reg_mV_per_mA: 0.018

* =============================================================
* TEST 2: STARTUP — Rload=5k, 300ms sim, BVDD ramp 10us
* =============================================================
* pvdd_peak (MAX 0-100ms) = 6.742587 V  at t=81.01us  [spec <= 5.5V — FAIL]
* t_start (WHEN V(pvdd)=4.5 RISE=1) = 31.86 us  [spec <= 100us — PASS]
startup_time_us: 31.86
startup_overshoot_V: 6.743

* =============================================================
* TEST 3: LOAD TRANSIENT — Rload=5k + Istep 9mA at 200ms (1us edge)
* 250ms simulation
* =============================================================
* v_before (avg 199-200ms) = 4.993251 V
* v_min    (MIN 200-205ms) = 1.565525 V  at t=201.36ms  [SEVERE UNDERSHOOT]
* v_max    (MAX 205-210ms) = 6.022490 V  at t=207.09ms  [SEVERE OVERSHOOT]
* v_after  (avg 248-250ms) = 4.993247 V  (recovers to regulation)
* undershoot = 4.993251 - 1.565525 = 3427.7 mV  [spec <= 150mV — FAIL]
* overshoot  = 6.022490 - 4.993251 = 1029.2 mV  [spec <= 150mV — FAIL]
undershoot_mV: 3428
overshoot_mV: 1029

* NOTE: The severe transient failure is a known loop bandwidth issue.
* The CG level shifter (startup v38) has limited slew on ea_out->gate path.
* With 1uF Cout, the 200ms startup charge is complete and the PVDD cap holds
* voltage briefly during the step, but the loop cannot respond fast enough
* (loop bandwidth ~5-10 Hz with this Cout) causing ~200ms of undershoot/recovery.

