* =============================================================
* ibvdd_avg (avg 250-300ms) = -1.441040e-4 A
* Sign convention: I(Vbvdd) negative in ngspice = source supplying current to circuit
* |ibvdd_avg| = 144.1 uA  [spec <= 300uA — PASS]
* (load current from 10Meg at ~4.993V = 0.499uA — negligible)
* vpvdd_iq = 4.993406 V (verified regulated during measurement window)
iq_active_uA: 144

